headline: Deere (DE): Exploring Valuation Following Latest Earnings and Revenue Growth
summary: Deere (DE) shares edged higher today following the company's latest financial update, which highlighted a modest rise in annual revenue along with a sharper increase in net income for the year. Investors are carefully weighing these results. See our latest analysis for Deere. Deere’s solid results have given the share price some fresh momentum, with a 2.3% jump today and a steady 16.5% year-to-date share price return. Still, total shareholder returns over the past year have trailed the S&P...
